{"tid":539690,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"尿好多泡可以點做？","createTime":"2018-01-24T18:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T21:47:19.000Z","uid":63460,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"98e789a885845b21cc2abd28026512463b2667ec","tid":539690,"uid":63460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:57:27.000Z","msg":"已經睇過四五次門診<br />\n<br />\n但係次次都係話冇咩事<br />\n<br />\n其實究竟係咪真係飲太少水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a3f47f858b4a97a5b155dcd1a4e15187a35f2d","tid":539690,"uid":24253,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:59:03.000Z","msg":"巴打小心係個腎有事導致痾蛋白尿 <br />\n另外，你有冇水腫？"},{"pid":"54afa50b36bb1215282a3b16b41fd3d7937b3323","tid":539690,"uid":108266,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:03:23.000Z","msg":"打側射落馬桶無咁多泡"},{"pid":"0d976bef078a335c6c7858605aa185e82de86fd1","tid":539690,"uid":165355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:05:55.000Z","msg":"多飲水 飲到啲尿變到清水咁清 你就會發現啲泡唔見哂"},{"pid":"7f33443c34b788bd9a3d90fb4e1303f79e7a759a","tid":539690,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:06:14.000Z","msg":"影張圖黎睇睇<br />\n認真<br />\n我都懷疑自己有蛋白尿"},{"pid":"de18dd84aea273a602c247690f37b410410a7fd0","tid":539690,"uid":63460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54afa50b36bb1215282a3b16b41fd3d7937b3323","tid":539690,"uid":108266,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:03:23.000Z","msg":"打側射落馬桶無咁多泡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:07:24.000Z","msg":"打得射係得少少"},{"pid":"8114b9fa77d99c903b83f2b7028b60e79e878361","tid":539690,"uid":63460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42a3f47f858b4a97a5b155dcd1a4e15187a35f2d","tid":539690,"uid":24253,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:59:03.000Z","msg":"巴打小心係個腎有事導致痾蛋白尿 <br />\n另外，你有冇水腫？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:07:48.000Z","msg":"水腫係咪即係突然間肥咗好多？"},{"pid":"17b0edb47131d82067a15142724787fd65133568","tid":539690,"uid":63460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f33443c34b788bd9a3d90fb4e1303f79e7a759a","tid":539690,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:06:14.000Z","msg":"影張圖黎睇睇<br />\n認真<br />\n我都懷疑自己有蛋白尿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:08:06.000Z","msg":"我搵緊我份report"},{"pid":"49d74d344354d03409e2d9b4bb9fc2e70183f6ec","tid":539690,"uid":152437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:17:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d71287a70bf9d029a4fcbb9ecde2ceeb2ba9c8cc","tid":539690,"uid":63460,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/25/031718_540f4b4cc412d297d436cd68a6c41820.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F25%2F031718_540f4b4cc412d297d436cd68a6c41820.png&h=909cddec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次驗就係咁樣有啲輕微<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/25/031719_c19696afa836eb76a4ef8697971e6059.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F25%2F031719_c19696afa836eb76a4ef8697971e6059.png&h=c3e3ac24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過多一個月第二次驗結果冇埋但係都係有泡先會去驗<br />\n<br />\n其實即係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好肯定係有泡"},{"pid":"3012b01cd53195f35b4a89990399373821d6b05b","tid":539690,"uid":50629,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:19:40.000Z","msg":"以前我都係咁 坐廁會用手隔一隔 水花無咁大感覺就無咁多泡 如果係公司會習慣jj貼落尿兜 會有水流落黎 順便洗乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d7e567d0672ed9c0053e3a754ec9e90fcc8c6b","tid":539690,"uid":63460,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"49d74d344354d03409e2d9b4bb9fc2e70183f6ec","tid":539690,"uid":152437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:17:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:20:09.000Z","msg":"個情況都成年啦應該唔係尿道炎<br />\n已經唔爭在懷疑自己係性病都驗埋啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/25/032004_4118fcd186d9db89cd6af052c701d4c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F25%2F032004_4118fcd186d9db89cd6af052c701d4c0.png&h=c0cd9732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5048a854651196f43058ec0c00fc153087479e89","tid":539690,"uid":54581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:34:34.000Z","msg":"醫生話無事<br />\n<br />\n你唔信可搵第二個醫生（但唔好講你之前個醫生點講）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對比下"},{"pid":"c4d075f48f84d3abb7a2e952f74f5b018d6c7115","tid":539690,"uid":58503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:35:44.000Z","msg":"我之前都係痾尿有泡，嗰陣去驗話有少少蛋白尿，跟住我再無理。幾年後，有晚左邊腰劇痛，之後去照x光發現生腎石。"},{"pid":"fabee0fc5ac278f2d0050c660ff3858b1d741fb0","tid":539690,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:37:48.000Z","msg":"打少啲飛機，早瞓，飲多啲水<br />\n一定係腎出事㗎啦"},{"pid":"0f09d42f7e855af73cc36e8b3cf635491ed44758","tid":539690,"uid":29649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:44:08.000Z","msg":"係咪打得飛機多又少飲水 same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c282d8c28c99b881a0aa86de09007c136067bd58","tid":539690,"uid":5764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d71287a70bf9d029a4fcbb9ecde2ceeb2ba9c8cc","tid":539690,"uid":63460,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/25/031718_540f4b4cc412d297d436cd68a6c41820.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F25%2F031718_540f4b4cc412d297d436cd68a6c41820.png&h=909cddec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次驗就係咁樣有啲輕微<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/25/031719_c19696afa836eb76a4ef8697971e6059.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F25%2F031719_c19696afa836eb76a4ef8697971e6059.png&h=c3e3ac24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過多一個月第二次驗結果冇埋但係都係有泡先會去驗<br />\n<br />\n其實即係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好肯定係有泡"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:55:42.000Z","msg":"你個醫生係咪有問題，你第一次小便比較多蛋白，第二次少啲但係都係有，可能要做一個microalbumin spot urine test or 24h urine protein test,我建議你都係睇腎科比較穩陣，我因為其他原因成日驗小便，測左好多次都係有蛋白尿，結果醫生轉介我睇腎科，做咗renal biopsy 確診腎小球炎"},{"pid":"00c257f21a5bf90a6c95f89081b5cbbc16bd66b8","tid":539690,"uid":5764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c282d8c28c99b881a0aa86de09007c136067bd58","tid":539690,"uid":5764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d71287a70bf9d029a4fcbb9ecde2ceeb2ba9c8cc","tid":539690,"uid":63460,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/25/031718_540f4b4cc412d297d436cd68a6c41820.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F25%2F031718_540f4b4cc412d297d436cd68a6c41820.png&h=909cddec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次驗就係咁樣有啲輕微<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/25/031719_c19696afa836eb76a4ef8697971e6059.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F25%2F031719_c19696afa836eb76a4ef8697971e6059.png&h=c3e3ac24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過多一個月第二次驗結果冇埋但係都係有泡先會去驗<br />\n<br />\n其實即係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好肯定係有泡"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:55:42.000Z","msg":"你個醫生係咪有問題，你第一次小便比較多蛋白，第二次少啲但係都係有，可能要做一個microalbumin spot urine test or 24h urine protein test,我建議你都係睇腎科比較穩陣，我因為其他原因成日驗小便，測左好多次都係有蛋白尿，結果醫生轉介我睇腎科，做咗renal biopsy 確診腎小球炎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:57:42.000Z","msg":"同埋呢兩次都係小便中有有紅血球，你最好去驗清楚紅血球係咪經過腎臟紅血球，但係唔係度度都有得做，例如養和醫院就有"},{"pid":"f9886d8bce791aeb7ce840bb4fa85446f61380ba","tid":539690,"uid":31962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T20:00:07.000Z","msg":"最準係留24小時尿去做test<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時食得多肉/運動完都會有少少多，但唔駛太擔心。<br />\n試下食清淡啲同埋戒奶有關野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n似多啲水休息多啲"},{"pid":"8fba9b351c1d734c8671fbd2cf491e50cfd97b8a","tid":539690,"uid":63460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c282d8c28c99b881a0aa86de09007c136067bd58","tid":539690,"uid":5764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d71287a70bf9d029a4fcbb9ecde2ceeb2ba9c8cc","tid":539690,"uid":63460,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/25/031718_540f4b4cc412d297d436cd68a6c41820.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F25%2F031718_540f4b4cc412d297d436cd68a6c41820.png&h=909cddec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次驗就係咁樣有啲輕微<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/25/031719_c19696afa836eb76a4ef8697971e6059.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F25%2F031719_c19696afa836eb76a4ef8697971e6059.png&h=c3e3ac24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過多一個月第二次驗結果冇埋但係都係有泡先會去驗<br />\n<br />\n其實即係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好肯定係有泡"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:55:42.000Z","msg":"你個醫生係咪有問題，你第一次小便比較多蛋白，第二次少啲但係都係有，可能要做一個microalbumin spot urine test or 24h urine protein test,我建議你都係睇腎科比較穩陣，我因為其他原因成日驗小便，測左好多次都係有蛋白尿，結果醫生轉介我睇腎科，做咗rena